data.description: Unique Northeast GJ area estate on 1.23 acres with main house PLUS additional guest cottage/ADU! Main house features an expansive 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom 2-story layout totaling 2,795 sq.ft., 575 sq. ft. garage, two living areas and two cozy fireplaces to enjoy! Upgraded kitchen offers the home chef an open and functional area to create culinary masterpieces with quartz countertops, large center island, premium stainless appliances (including double oven & gas range), lovely backsplash, plentiful cabinet storage and large pantry space! Adjacent seating area is perfect for entertaining and the separate formal dining area features tray ceiling and plant of natural sunlight throughout! Primary suite on the main level with en-suite bathroom that offers dual vanities with quartz counters, freestanding soaker tub, newer tile floors and comfortable walk-in shower. Large laundry room on main level offers convenient wash sink, cabinet storage and separate countertop folding area. Upper level offers three additional bedrooms and full bath with dual vanities and a tub/shower combo! The guest cottage, built in 2007 has 1,192 sq. ft. with 616 sq. ft. garage. Living room, 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, laundry, kitchen, sun porch and lots of storage; perfect space to utilize as short term income producing property or long-term rental! Spacious flagstone patio off the ADU; perfect place for a fire pit and outdoor entertaining area for guests! Incredibly landscaped yard features a pergola-covered deck that's the prefect space to enjoy our Colorado climate and amazing Grand Valley views! Irrigation water through Palisade District for ease of watering; complete sprinkler system on property with new irrigation pump  Plenty of RV parking space to comfortably store your OHV & recreational vehicles! Three large sheds on the property that allow for even more useful storage space!
